Enum Class Brand

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Brand>
com.example.mco2_supermarketsimulator.Brand
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Brand>, Constable
public enum Brand extends Enum<Brand>
These are the different types of brands for the productTypes, hence a BREAD can come from "Crustory" or "LoafLuxe".
